Oh - oh my - well my brother - my mother didn't always get there with the children but my father was a strict church goer, twice a day. Always, always twice a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3488920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 Which denomination?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9124922 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 Oh we belonged to the Unit
ed Free Church of Scotland. There were the established church on the island and the United Free Church. We went to the United Free Church.
