\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9124922 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 No, not with the church. No, there wasn't very much, no. Not very much. With the churches.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3488920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 Was there a choir?
