old out of - he had measles and he went to soon out of Winston Churchill's funeral to see the procession, he went too thinly clad and he got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16545636\charrsid14301207 pneumonia}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
