\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3488920 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 And to the bridegroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9124922 JL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14894142\charrsid14301207 And - and - and - and then - to him he would say, and boy, sit the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701494\charrsid14301207 re}{
