u know, that most men was - was - was - was - when they got, you know, they - they - they were a sort of a virile race you know. Maybe some of those girls would get into - into trouble you know latterly. Then you have to be taken before the session to get
 
church - privileges, you know, to get the communion. And the head - they would stand up, stand up and say to the - to the - to the minister, now, be merciful - to the young people. They were at a wedding, and this happened in the long bed. So that - so he
 - they would take a - a comparatively - lenient view of this and they would say all right, if that's the case then we should have to - carry on, come to the church. But now -
