e, could you not come inside? The man said, no, I'm not coming in. I - I - I knew - I saw in the window that you'd been gutting the fish and you'd be out with the cleanings - the guts of the fish so I knowed you would be here so I was just waiting here. O
h
, he says, that's a cold night, you could come in. And set you down. No, he said, thank you, I'm - I'll not. Well, he says, do you - who - are you waiting on anybody? He said, it's you I'm waiting on. You. Well, what - what did you have to me? Well, he sa
